snippet.title: Rain World Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rain-world/project-rain-world

Rain World is a challenging survival platformer set in an exotic alien land where deadly rains sweep the surface, obliterating all in their path. Currently in development for PC and Mac. Since YouTube quality sucks, please check out the HD trailer on vimeo: https://vimeo.com/81965682

concept, art, design & programming by Joar Jakobsson 
http://joarportfolio.com/

music & trailer by James Primate 
http://jamesprimate.tk

now on greenlight! http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=213453611
